item.title: Abstract submission
item.description: If you are interested to send a contribution, please submit your abstract via EasyChair ( https://easychair.org/conferences/?conf=econet2018 ). You can indicate on the abstract whether you want to contribute with a 15-min talk or whether you prefer giving a 5-min ignite.
